Text: Half of the songs from the first and second albums wouldn't play for me. Other wise no complaints. good quality otherwise.

I like HCTM too much to upload their cd's, but I will put their performance on the Bob and Tom radio show up.  Hopefully, people like the music from it and go *buy* the cd's.  That's how I first heard about them, and it got me hooked.

Here Come The Mummies Sound kind of interesting. A friend of mine set them up somewhere up north. They said go on and boot leg their music they get pennies off record sales, but live shows and merch they make their bank off of!!! Just throwing that out there guys! Peace!
